    <item>
      <title>官方媒体称朝鲜进行首次“核触发”模拟演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜国家通讯社朝中社周二表示，朝鲜在领导人金正恩的指导下进行了首次核反击演习，以模拟其“核触发”管理系统，这是对其敌人的明确警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-nuclear-counterattack-simulation-drills-kcna-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:37:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰央行不同意监管机构关于资本设置的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealands-central-bank-disagrees-with-watchdog-over-capital-settings-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行周二表示，不同意该国竞争监管机构关于其审慎资本设置需要审查的评估。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealands-central-bank-disagrees-with-watchdog-over-capital-settings-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国谴责朝鲜最新的弹道导弹发射</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-condemns-north-koreas-latest-ballistic-missile-launch-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国表示，朝鲜周一发射弹道导弹后违反了多项联合国安理会决议，并呼吁平壤“停止此类挑衅”并“重返对话”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-condemns-north-koreas-latest-ballistic-missile-launch-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾发生6.3级地震，目前尚无受损报告</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾气象部门表示，周二，台湾东部花莲县发生了 6.3 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-63-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
